ActOther Than Statutory Authority
SubjectOrder Revoking Order in Council P.C. 1995-2004
PrecisOrder (1) revoking Order in Council P.C. 1995-2004 of November 28, 1995; (2) determining as special service, within the meaning of those Regulations, service that meets certains conditions; and (3) specifiying that the Bar that is awarded with the SPECIAL SERVICE MEDAL, representing the special service referred to in paragraph (b) is to bear the words "PEACE - PAIX".
